text: My first time visiting this church. Upon entering at 9:40am, there were so many walking out after the earlier morning service. Lots of people, young and old, English and Chinese speaking. I can recall childhood memories of this place only, although I've never step into here.
Accessible by wheelchair, this new building spots friendly greeters and members. The basement holds a columbarium - Garden of Eternal Peace. FAITH Kindergarten can also be found on Lecel 2.
I really enjoyed my time here.  Highly recommend.
Pleasant ambience, serene, convenient and accessible. Nice main worship hall!
A place where GOD ask me to go! Unto HIM be The GLORY in CHRIST JESUS our Mighty GOD and Creator!Amen.
